    "description": "<p><strong>Our World is Your Playground.</strong></p>\n<p>A world-class lifestyle hotel in the heart of Orchard Road, where playfulness meets peak performance; creativity meets innovation; business meets success. At Pullman Singapore Orchard, we don’t do ordinary. Pioneering and stylish, guests can push their boundaries in 326 &nbsp;guestrooms and suites, trendsetting F&amp;B outlets and immersive relaxation zones; not to mention the happening lobby.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Pullman Singapore Orchard opens its doors and taking the Orchard Road experience to the next level. Challenging the status quo, we are redefining hospitality with seamless, fun, cool and smart interactions.</p>",
